Notes: W. Bauer says positive knowledge from 17 schools between Hunterville and Island Bay except for one in Auckland (lots of migrants), 2 from Nelson, 1 from Cheviot. Liz Gordon says it is known in Ch'ch & Timaru. High consistency from Wellington. Harry thought it might be a skate-boarding term. Laurie Bauer says an American quote called something "scungy & grody" and thought it might be a nice blend of those two words.
